  "title": "CONDO + Office CLEANER",
  "description": "<p>Required to handle 2 site. ( One at Lavender( In Morning ) , One at east coast( In Afternoon) <br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform general cleaning tasks such as:<br />Sweeping, mopping, vacuuming, and dusting<br />Cleaning and disinfecting restrooms, pantries, and common areas<br />Emptying bins and replacing liners<br />Replenishing toilet and cleaning supplies</li><li>Follow daily cleaning schedules and site-specific SOPs</li><li>Ensure all work areas are kept neat and safe</li><li>Report any maintenance issues or irregularities to supervisors</li><li>Use cleaning equipment and chemicals safely and correctly</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Experience is added point</li><li>Physically fit and able to work on your feet</li><li>Able to follow instructions and work as part of a team</li><li>Responsible and punctual</li><li><u><strong>Required to handle 2 site. ( One at Lavender , One at east coast) </strong></u></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary</li><li>Full-time role</li><li>Paid training and clear work processes</li><li>Immediate start available</li><li>Uniform and equipment provided</li><li>Opportunities for career advancement (e.g. to Supervisor roles)</li></ul><p><strong>Work Schedule</strong></p><ul><li>8am - 6pm<br />(<em>Exact hours may vary based on site. Split shifts available in some locations.</em>)</li></ul><p><strong>Apply Now</strong></p><p>Send your details via WhatsApp to +65 8688 7869</p>",
